public @interface Wip
    Work in progress feature. The feature in this state will not be removed, is subject to signature and name changes, but they may occurs less often than Alpha and Beta. A feature in Wip state may receive a lot of improvements and refinements before the ready state. This is a marker annotation, the intention of this annotation is to provide a reference of development state of a feature, but not to enable, disable or provide features, neither to add more than a reference.
